data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value:
select "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."WorkOrderTimeSheetId", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."FkWorkOrderID", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."FkEmpID", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."StartDate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."EndDate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."StartTime", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."EndTime", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."Day", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."WorkStatus", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."Breake", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."IsRamadan", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."IsInvoiced", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."InvoiceNumber", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."WorkHrs", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."Remarks", "EmployeesList"."EmpName", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."IsChecked", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."CheckedBy", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."CheckedDate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."IsApproved", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."ApprovedBy", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."ApprovedDate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."HourlyRate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."OTRate", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."NormalWorkingHours", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."RamadanWorkingHours", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."OTWorkingHours", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."TotalWorkingPrice", "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."TotalAdditionalPrice", '1' as "Qty", 'Hour' as "OT Unit", "WorkOrderInvoice"."FkInvoiceId", Case "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."WorkStatus" When 'Holiday' then 'H' when 'Duty' then 'D' when 'Absent' then 'A' End, Case "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."ShiftStatus" When 1 then 'D' when 2 then 'N' End as ShiftStatus
from ("dbo"."WorkOrderTimeSheet" "WorkOrderTimeSheet" inner join "dbo"."EmployeesList" "EmployeesList" on ("EmployeesList"."EmpID" = "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."FkEmpID") inner join "dbo"."WorkOrderInvoice" "WorkOrderInvoice" on ("WorkOrderInvoice"."FkWorkOrderId" = "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."FkWorkOrderID")) where ("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."StartDate" between "WorkOrderInvoice"."StartDate" And "WorkOrderInvoice"."EndDate") And "WorkOrderTimeSheet"."IsInvoiced" =1

data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value:
select distinct "Invoice"."InvoiceId", "Invoice"."InvoiceNumber", "Invoice"."InvoiceDate", "Invoice"."InvoiceRefNo", "Invoice"."FKJobOrderMasterID", "Invoice"."SRTTotal", "Invoice"."TSTotal", "Invoice"."InvoiceTotal", "Invoice"."Disount", "Invoice"."NetAmount", "Invoice"."ProvideDescription", "Invoice"."InvoiceStartDate", "Invoice"."InvoiceEndDate", "JobOrderMaster"."JobOrderNumber", "ProjectsList"."ProjectName", "CustomersList"."CustomerName", "TestsList"."TestName", "JobOrderMaster"."ExpiryDate", "JobOrderMaster"."TransactionDate", "WorkOrderInvoice"."FkWorkOrderId", "PriceUnitList"."UnitType", "WorkOrderList"."FKJobOrderDetailsID", "WorkOrderList"."WorkOrderNo",WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID, "WorkOrderList"."RegularWorkHrs", "WorkOrderList"."RamadanWorkHrs", "WorkOrderList"."MonthlyRate", "WorkOrderList"."UnitOfAddition", "WorkOrderList"."ExtraWorkHourRate", "WorkOrderList"."NightShiftPerc","WorkOrderList"."SiteName", "WorkOrderList"."Description", "WorkOrderList"."TransDate",ISNULL(n.NigthDays,0) as NigthDays ,(ISNULL(n.NigthAmount,0) * ISNULL("WorkOrderList"."NightShiftPerc",0))/100 as NightShiftPercAmount ,nn.Sum_OTRate,nn.Sum_OTWorkingHours,nn.Sum_TotalAdditionalPrice,nn.Sum_WorkHrs,nn.Sum_TotalWorkingPrice from ((((((((("dbo"."Invoice" "Invoice" inner join "dbo"."JobOrderMaster" "JobOrderMaster" on ("JobOrderMaster"."JobOrderMasterID" = "Invoice"."FKJobOrderMasterID")) inner join "dbo"."ProjectsList" "ProjectsList" on ("ProjectsList"."ProjectID" = "JobOrderMaster"."FKProjectID")) inner join "dbo"."CustomersList" "CustomersList" on ("CustomersList"."CustomerID" = "JobOrderMaster"."FKCustomerID")) inner join "dbo"."JobOrderDetails" "JobOrderDetails" on ("JobOrderDetails"."FKJobOrderMasterID" = "JobOrderMaster"."JobOrderMasterID")) inner join "dbo"."TestsList" "TestsList" on ("TestsList"."TestID" = "JobOrderDetails"."FKTestID")) inner join "dbo"."WorkOrderInvoice" "WorkOrderInvoice" on ("WorkOrderInvoice"."FkInvoiceId" = "Invoice"."InvoiceId")) inner join "dbo"."PriceUnitList" "PriceUnitList" on ("PriceUnitList"."PriceUnitID" = "JobOrderDetails"."FKPriceUnitID")) inner join "dbo"."WorkOrderList" "WorkOrderList" on (("WorkOrderList"."FKJobOrderDetailsID" = "JobOrderDetails"."JobOrderDetailsID") and ("WorkOrderList"."WorkOrderID" = "WorkOrderInvoice"."FkWorkOrderId"))) inner join "dbo"."WorkOrderTimeSheet" "WorkOrderTimeSheet" on ("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."FkWorkOrderID" = "WorkOrderList"."WorkOrderID")) left join ( SELECT Invoice.InvoiceId, WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID,count(WorkOrderTimeSheet.TotalAdditionalPrice) as NigthDays,Sum( WorkOrderTimeSheet.TotalAdditionalPrice)+ Sum( WorkOrderTimeSheet.TotalWorkingPrice) as NigthAmount FROM Invoice INNER JOIN WorkOrderInvoice ON Invoice.InvoiceId = WorkOrderInvoice.FkInvoiceId INNER JOIN WorkOrderList ON WorkOrderInvoice.FkWorkOrderId = WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID INNER JOIN WorkOrderTimeSheet ON WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID = WorkOrderTimeSheet.FkWorkOrderID
where WorkOrderTimeSheet.ShiftStatus=2 group by Invoice.InvoiceId, WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID ) N on n.InvoiceId="Invoice"."InvoiceId" and n.WorkOrderID=WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID
left join ( SELECT Invoice.InvoiceId, WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID,sum("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."WorkHrs") as "Sum_WorkHrs", sum("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."OTRate") as "Sum_OTRate", sum("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."OTWorkingHours") as "Sum_OTWorkingHours", sum("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."TotalWorkingPrice") as "Sum_TotalWorkingPrice", sum("WorkOrderTimeSheet"."TotalAdditionalPrice") as "Sum_TotalAdditionalPrice", Sum( WorkOrderTimeSheet.TotalAdditionalPrice) TotalAdditionalPrice,Sum( WorkOrderTimeSheet.TotalWorkingPrice) as TotalWorkingPrice FROM Invoice INNER JOIN WorkOrderInvoice ON Invoice.InvoiceId = WorkOrderInvoice.FkInvoiceId INNER JOIN WorkOrderList ON WorkOrderInvoice.FkWorkOrderId = WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID INNER JOIN WorkOrderTimeSheet ON WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID = WorkOrderTimeSheet.FkWorkOrderID where WorkOrderTimeSheet.StartDate between "WorkOrderInvoice"."StartDate" And "WorkOrderInvoice"."EndDate" group by Invoice.InvoiceId, WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID ) NN on NN.InvoiceId="Invoice"."InvoiceId" and NN.WorkOrderID=WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID where ("PriceUnitList"."UnitType" = 1) order by Invoice.InvoiceId, WorkOrderList.WorkOrderID
